  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c987814e-b469-4d37-8581-fb786012c6ba\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dadd452a-aa7f-464e-940d-99adf3ea4987\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-28304057-4832-415f-a2f7-f946cde1e8f6\"><b>안녕하세요 남성역 한의원 이수한의원입니다!</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-c987814e-b469-4d37-8581-fb786012c6ba\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5c8d2443-1a9c-4a07-9661-678bfd583227\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"11\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_11.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7dac5bf8-1a69-428f-a39c-c23a9ddf3faf\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9874ae2b-32f4-4a74-814d-0f028809e1ad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummyeongjo   \" id=\"SE-039aa2db-52b0-40be-848b-2293e694ea19\"><b>아이 키, 언제부터 신경 써야 할까요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6ac98ce7-1f9f-4d93-bed8-c98a981f143d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c24cabdd-2c38-4fab-8ccf-430550af8618\">우리 아이 키 성장은 단순히 유전만으로 결정되지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-837c51a3-8d85-42b4-a039-ab3e40d8669d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-91da28f5-05a5-40f1-8eca-e19dfd7b9c0a\"><b>남자아이는 초등학교 4학년, 여자아이는 초등학교 3학년 무렵</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-80694d0d-f7d8-4cc3-8f25-15347973d242\">이 골든타임!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2a509852-375b-46ba-90ca-21dea3e9325a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7f4be4a1-7250-4301-ba06-65ad7fa7a960\">성장판이 닫히기 전, 지금이 바로 성장 치료와 관리의 적기입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-7dac5bf8-1a69-428f-a39c-c23a9ddf3faf\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-cb6c352b-4774-4945-9f0d-63ef6e00b6ef\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-97529a27-2ad7-491b-97da-65332c6dc73c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-97529a27-2ad7-491b-97da-65332c6dc73c\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6e48b588344aabb7.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1700\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1700\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6e48b588344aabb7.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6e48b588344aabb7.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-97529a27-2ad7-491b-97da-65332c6dc73c\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-238b29a3-c5b5-4b3b-8cf9-7503c05c93c9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-da7d4d26-708e-458f-9632-f0df656e83d7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ca7b8399-b5fe-4c22-aae4-cc90b3a5af6f\"><b>성장호르몬은 언제 많이 나올까요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fead0978-4a24-409b-85e0-be83ed010d45\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cbec1e24-db48-43d7-af74-c127784c75d4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-004f364a-63b9-4359-90b3-10a2b67af1bb\">성장호르몬은 밤에 깊이 잠든 시간, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d41edb2c-c2e7-45ad-a2d4-0bc1e0b2e1ca\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6820f69e-442d-4add-85ff-9537c2b9faaf\">특히 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e477896d-61d4-416d-8513-bed08b1fe4f6\"><b>밤 10시부터 새벽 2시 사이</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-84180b7a-98ed-49de-b0ef-65708bfab4ab\">에 가장 활발히 분비됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-84f5e771-4d32-4a8e-a76b-a0d0b07ce9b6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ef8306c8-5db0-4078-b984-cdb9cf36dff0\">따라서 규칙적인 수면 습관을 들이는 것이 키 성장에 매우 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-fead0978-4a24-409b-85e0-be83ed010d45\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-a8ee3556-21b6-427f-8bc9-a3582d3ad9ab\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-153c0466-a059-4ba1-87c9-cfd26b7a6ee0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-81ffe61a-aef8-4998-a2bd-2801403bf001\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-65b5e6fc-36fd-4ea1-b3ec-72b529541f89\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-153c0466-a059-4ba1-87c9-cfd26b7a6ee0\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-d90cbf15-2cf0-4f72-adcc-fc0dfb22cc50\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dbd7b064-fbcf-4664-a8ff-4e8b2e121108\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d3f8ec16-78a0-44b3-a21d-2f2aebfcc298\"><b>성조숙증과 키 성장의 관계</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a2754b7a-13c7-42b6-8d68-4e56eb833e5d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dd325696-6baf-4b95-8760-fc356291c8e6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fd7d5bba-0565-496d-8b72-737cac5a137a\">요즘 아이들에게 흔히 나타나는 성조숙증은 성장판을 빨리 닫히게 만들어 성장을 방해할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-342c9bc1-44f7-4134-b3c4-b870fdfc34a0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3032deea-2795-4051-a150-ffbf3bac5b87\">특히 여아의 경우 이른 초경, 남아의 경우 변성기 시작이 빠르면 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a8f912fb-5453-405d-ac84-f95c5185859b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5b6a5dc7-5f1a-41cf-9746-0b0a1945ec6f\"><b>최종 키가 작아질 위험</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d92442ed-6b4b-4264-b88f-b0e5084acdbd\">이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cced0804-b27e-4151-ab00-1ed36e8d1f66\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-70d80585-d4a5-404a-92dc-7c46e1bdc34d\">조기 발견과 관리가 필요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-a2754b7a-13c7-42b6-8d68-4e56eb833e5d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-db71865a-3996-40c7-a601-58e08246cd7e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-a111fb24-5e0d-4130-a599-072ee8e3abd3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-834842fc-bec6-4e33-a3b5-3367ffc12a94\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e6a10d82-332b-44b4-b16a-c3e6285d8b3f\"><b>한의학에서 보는 성장 원리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dc6ef50c-45fa-4632-bf0b-8da7e60b7ac9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-66792086-56df-42ab-acc9-48943038accb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-470a1089-4e27-4464-a8f2-c0e201d57875\">한의학에서는 성장의 핵심을 간(肝)·신(腎)·비(脾)의 균형에서 찾습니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a52e99cb-4145-4dde-b3c6-1e6a3720f548\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-15fb9a06-5fb4-481a-b7b6-4d89e4bb352b\"><b>간(肝)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4624c7db-92b6-41f8-84ee-d5354a2a60cd\">: 혈액을 저장하고 근육과 인대를 튼튼히 함 → 성장판 보호</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a8a9bf96-9ac0-420e-bd23-9914180b7f1b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-37848836-0ec1-4e9c-8cbe-b3232a791352\"><b>신(腎)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-058ab2f7-b1a2-4716-acaa-33206234b47a\">: 뼈와 골수의 발달을 주관 → 키 성장의 기본 에너지</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-afa1439e-443c-49f6-baac-9a44f4bc6697\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-37407998-af3f-4dbb-91e2-bc2908ef613b\"><b>비(脾)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9053c21b-1916-4d48-8826-c9a835bcc360\">: 소화·흡수를 담당 → 성장에 필요한 영양 공급</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1ee0518b-e96e-458a-8ad1-153c42e51d67\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8c3da29b-7914-4a6a-b631-44bcd1675f1c\">따라서 성장 클리닉에서는 아이의 체질과 상태에 맞춰 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b2474bb6-3db1-4418-b6df-2e7ecd0cf347\"><b>한약, 침, 뜸 치료, 생활습관 지도</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-75119420-fbbc-4272-83a2-3211dab82914\">를 통해 성장판을 지켜줍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-dc6ef50c-45fa-4632-bf0b-8da7e60b7ac9\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-9b6a52ca-f9c8-4357-85ef-401eb9b0adec\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-758916ec-bc8d-4196-a363-d62c2a0d0757\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6b4bf2d5-471f-427c-b41e-1fd3d880fbb9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6fb41c7b-97dc-4dff-a675-519c2e06ef53\"><b>부모가 꼭 챙겨야 할 생활습관</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dc85f451-6ab5-451e-a7f0-2fbc6a8dde65\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2c1c3308-f684-49f6-a322-dc965df9a9db\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5acf98e3-a5d8-4a0f-b5af-05cc7242a68d\">충분한 숙면 (밤 10시 이전 취침)</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-59365fb8-6c0b-4552-92f0-ecee048dd045\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c8795e55-a100-4795-870e-7c093234e018\">균형 잡힌 식사 (단백질·칼슘·아연 풍부한 음식)</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-541f0eee-eec7-45bf-bad7-b95f1c3955d2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-84d68473-998e-43e0-9267-962a29091823\">규칙적인 운동 (줄넘기, 스트레칭, 성장체조)</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-17db56fc-0bdd-4a6b-a7d0-0b6dcb4f9b9b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ee837f4a-d285-4093-8c44-274dc6a03783\">스마트폰·게임 줄이고 바른 자세 유지</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-dc85f451-6ab5-451e-a7f0-2fbc6a8dde65\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7a2ef987-2952-49b8-b7b8-8f5f8080daf5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7a2ef987-2952-49b8-b7b8-8f5f8080daf5\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/994b541450245e35.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1536\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/994b541450245e35.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/994b541450245e35.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"750\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-7a2ef987-2952-49b8-b7b8-8f5f8080daf5\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-d93a37f9-7f79-4b23-b4bc-d2e17df73383\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b1295aa8-22ab-41c0-93e0-705be4d2cb0a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-905571b8-6af8-49a9-ad94-18247a00e696\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummyeongjo se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-7b986ceb-2b05-40f4-867f-99526814abee\">아이의 키 성장은 골든타임을 놓치지 않는 것이 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-79c133de-b84c-4bb8-aeaf-a681dea85bee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummyeongjo se-weight-unset se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-85caf81c-83d1-46bc-bdd3-f8641f5786e3\">가장 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a3507147-df30-4a0c-b116-677662e674b1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d1c4689e-8dd5-429b-9df2-e7fc36182c7a\">지금부터라도 생활습관을 바로잡고, 체질에 맞는 한방 관리로 성장판을 지켜준다면 아이의 키 성장은 충분히 도와줄 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0133f023-2012-434b-ad17-18fb87c76a1c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b30cc6a0-ffd8-4e54-a048-3cb1a905fcfd\">이수한의원에서 우리 아이의 성장 가능성을 확인해보세요!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-b1295aa8-22ab-41c0-93e0-705be4d2cb0a\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align-center se-l-default\" >\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-7139a15f-bb8e-4fff-ba0c-1aa58202ed03\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_video\", \"id\" :\"SE-7139a15f-bb8e-4fff-ba0c-1aa58202ed03\", \"data\" : { \"videoType\" : \"player\", \"vid\" : \"17CCEBCC21A13F8B0C94141B435665847E88\", \"inkey\" : \"V12655e71400208866427fc00f15df45674a3e1015640fbced4f727e581eedabb2b57fc00f15df45674a3\", \"thumbnail\": \"https://phinf.pstatic.net/image.nmv/blog_2025_09_03_2810/8Xez9q1n5j_01.jpg\", \"originalWidth\": \"1080\", \"originalHeight\": \"1920\", \"width\": \"500\", \"height\": \"888\", \"contentMode\": \"fit\", \"format\": \"normal\", \"mediaMeta\": {\"@ctype\":\"mediaMeta\",\"title\":\"성장\",\"tags\":[],\"description\":null}, \"useServiceData\": \"false\"}}' data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_video\", \"id\": \"SE-7139a15f-bb8e-4fff-ba0c-1aa58202ed03\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"video\", \"ai\": \"false\", \"videoType\": \"player\", \"vid\": \"17CCEBCC21A13F8B0C94141B435665847E88\", \"inkey\": \"V1280a542d1905f574a93fc00f15df45674a3e1015640fbced4f727e581eedabb2b57fc00f15df45674a3\", \"thumbnail\": \"https://phinf.pstatic.net/image.nmv/blog